                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-361-off1951 t18300415-361-cd1952"></join>. 1 table-spoon, value 16s., and 1 fork, value 7s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18300415-361-victim2984" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Abbott
                        <interp inst="t18300415-361-victim2984" type="surname" value="Abbott"></interp>
