            </rs>. Aged 16. - <rs id="t18300415-361-punish1957" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300415-361-punish1957" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-361-defend2982 t18300415-361-punish1957"></join>
               Confined Six Months
            </rs>.</p>
